This is a Processing sketch and is work in progress.

Requirements:
=============

1. Processing 1.1+: www.processing.org
2. GSVideo: From http://gsvideo.sourceforge.net/
        i. Extract the files to the $SKETCHBOOK/libraries folder
        ii. Remember to restart Processing

Currently, the video is recorded in the OGG format.

HowTo
=====

While running:
1. To take screenshots: Press 's'.
2. To start/stop recording a video: Press ' ' (space).


